		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wonder if it might be possible to reduce the wiring by just disconnecting the high address line from the Cx4 and feeding that directly into the ROM chip (so the Cx4 thinks it's always within the 16Mbit memory space and doesn't tri-state the data lines).

		

